  ${
    $d a f l F $.  $d a f l J $.  $d a f l X $.  $d f Y $.
    flimval.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    flimval.2 $e |- Y = U. F $.
    $( The set of limit points of a filter.  (Contributed by Jeff Hankins,
       4-Sep-2009.) $)
    flimval $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ F e. Fil /\ X = Y ) -> ( ( fLim ` J ) ` F ) =
